data.description: Your dream home awaits! Fall in love with this stylish, spacious & beautifully updated, two-story, 4bed/2.5 bath home, nestled in the established & quiet Adams Hill neighborhood with NO HOA!! The home's elegant brick exterior opens to a spacious living room with a beautiful brick, wood burning fireplace & abundant natural light throughout. Your stylish kitchen features granite countertops, lots of cabinet space, and separate breakfast and formal dining areas. The serene owner's retreat is privately situated away from the other bedrooms, with vaulted ceilings & a decked-out en suite featuring dual vanity & a luxurious stand up shower. Home offers the ideal layout for hosting guests inside & out, with a covered patio in your private backyard, situated on close to a quarter acre. Great location with easy access to major highways, yet tucked away in a quiet neighborhood, offering the perfect balance of tranquility & convenience. Minutes from HEB, Costco, shopping & dining, and walking distance to the elementary school in highly rated NISD! Come tour it today and make it your Home Sweet Home! New Roof & HVAC in 2022
